          <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent 45%,rgba(26,32,44,0.72));"></div>
          <div style="position:absolute;bottom:24px;left:24px;right:24px;">
            <p style="color:#81E6D9;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 6px;">Legally Recognised</p>
            <p style="color:#fff;font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;margin:0;">End-to-end marriage certificate attestation for UAE and abroad</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
        <p style="color:#2D3748;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:0.75rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:28px;height:1px;background:#2D3748;"></span>Overview</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:900;color:#1A202C;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 18px;">Marriage Certificate Attestation</h2>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;">Marriage certificate attestation in the UAE is an essential process for couples who intend to live, work, or settle in the country. It involves verifying the authenticity and validity of the marriage certificate issued in the home country.</p>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;">It is essential to go through the attestation procedure since it guarantees that the marriage certificate will be approved and legally recognised by UAE authorities. The procedure typically involves notarization of the marriage certificate, followed by authentication from the respective state authorities and the Ministry of External Affairs (MEA) in the home country.</p>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px;">Subsequently, the marriage certificate is attested by the UAE embassy or consulate in the home country, and finally, it undergoes verification by the Ministry of Foreign Affairs (MOFA) in the UAE.</p>
        <div style="background:#F0FFFE;border:1px solid #B2F5EA;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;">
          <p style="color:#1A202C;font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 4px;">Index Office Services</p>
          <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:0.98rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">We provide quick and effortless service in <a href="https://helplinegroupuae.com/marriage-registration/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#1A202C;font-weight:700;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:#38B2AC;text-underline-offset:3px;">marriage registration</a> and certificate attestation with our experts. We have 25 years of experience.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ WHAT IS A MARRIAGE CERTIFICATE ════ -->
<section style="background:#F8FAFF;padding:76px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(45,55,72,0.02) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(45,55,72,0.02) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:44px 44px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:600px;height:400px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(56,178,172,0.07) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>

  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="two-col" style="display:flex;gap:52px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">

      <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
        <p style="color:#2D3748;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:0.75rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:28px;height:1px;background:#2D3748;"></span>Legal Document</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3vw,2.1rem);font-weight:900;color:#1A202C;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 16px;">What is a Marriage Certificate?</h2>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px;">A marriage certificate is a legal proof of marriage issued by a government agency or marriage register after a couple has solemnized their marriage. It contains details like spouse names, wedding date and location, and witnesses or officiants.</p>
        <p style="color:#4B5563;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:24px;">The certificate is essential for legal rights, obligations, changing surnames, receiving spousal benefits, and paying joint taxes.</p>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px;">
          {["Spouse names","Wedding date & location","Witnesses or officiants","Legal rights & obligations","Changing surnames","Spousal benefits"].map(item => (
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:10px 14px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e7ef;border-radius:10px;font-size:0.98rem;color:#1A202C;font-weight:500;">
              <span style="width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#38B2AC;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="10" height="10"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              </span>
              {item}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:380px;">
        <img src="/images/img-78.webp" alt="Marriage certificate document" style="width:100%;height:320px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:20px;box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);" />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════ HOW TO / TWO TABS ════ -->
<section style="background:#fff;padding:76px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,transparent,transparent 48px,rgba(56,178,172,0.04) 48px,rgba(56,178,172,0.04) 49px);pointer-events:none;z-index:0;"></div>
